                                   DateTimeDt theSince,

        Description copied from interface: IGenericClient
        Implementation of the "history instance" method.
        Specified by:
        history in interface IGenericClient
        Parameters:
        theType - The type of resource to return the history for, or null to search for history across all resources
        theSince - If not null, request that the server only return resources updated since this time
        theLimit - If not null, request that the server return no more than this number of resources. Note that the server may return less even if more are available, but should not return more according to the FHIR specification.
        Returns:
        A bundle containing returned resources
